  <title>Trajectory lines</title>

  <para>
    <informalfigure><screenshot><mediaobject><imageobject>
      <imagedata fileref="images/scene_objects/trajectory_lines_example.gif" format="GIF" scale="60" />
    </imageobject></mediaobject></screenshot></informalfigure>
    A trajectory lines <link linkend="scene_objects">data object</link> stores the continuous motion paths of a set of particles,
    which have been precomputed by a <link linkend="particles.modifiers.generate_trajectory_lines">Generate trajectory lines</link> modifier
    for the purpose of visualization. 
  </para>
  <para>
    The visual appearance of the trajectory lines in rendered images is controlled through the associated 
    <link linkend="visual_elements.trajectory_lines">Trajectory lines</link> visual element.
  </para>

